  <brief_title>Postoperative Pain Management in Hospital and Following Discharge From Hospital.</brief_title>
  <official_title>Assessment of Postoperative Pain Management in Patients Undergoing Total Knee Arthroplasty Immediately After Surgery and Following Discharge From Hospital.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
